While researching about cybercrime, I found it astonishing to know how easily people can fall prey to UPI scams because of their unawareness. People assume that by filling in their UPI PIN, they can receive money, but this is completely false.

While completing this task, I learned how important it is to be careful while dealing with online transactions. One habit I will adopt is never to approve any unknown transaction or scan any unknown QR code. I will also try to spread awareness among my friends and family regarding such scams to help them avoid such cybercrimes.
